        "generateUrl": "https://docs.onsched.com/docs/client-credentials",
        "setup": "Log into the OnSched dashboard and open **API Settings** / **Client Credentials**. Create or copy your `client_id` and `client_secret`, then use them with `POST /v3/oauth/token` using the `client_credentials` grant. The docs recommend this flow for server-to-server integrations. Access tokens are short-lived (about 60 minutes).",
