        "generateUrl": "https://docs.onsched.com/docs/client-credentials",
        "setup": "In the v3 dashboard, create or copy the public client ID used by unauthenticated/public routes. The docs say it is sent as `x-client-id` and is intended only for `/v3/public/*` endpoints such as public availability and appointment flows.",
